Fraud Alert
Hunt is aware that unauthorized individuals/organizations are using Hunt's name and logo to solicit potential job-seekers for employment by sending out false employment offers and other fraudulent recruitment materials in an attempt to defraud job applicants.
Hunt is also aware of websites which imitate the Hunt website and make use of Hunt's name and logo, and other intellectual property, in an unauthorized manner. Please be advised that Hunt is not affiliated with Krust Oil and Gas, Ltd., NorthCo Oil & Gas or ZenGas Oil & Gas Company in any way. If you receive a solicitation from any of these entities for personal information, or if you have any concerns regarding the legitimacy or authenticity of any communications, please email your concerns to fraudalert@huntoil.com.
Please be advised that Hunt Consolidated, Inc. and its affiliated companies would never ask potential job seekers for any sort of advance payments during the recruitment and employment process. If any person or agency solicits money from you as part of the recruitment/employment process, or as part of an offer of employment, you should assume that the communication is fraudulent and not from Hunt Consolidated, Inc., its affiliates or any agency representing Hunt Consolidated, Inc.Hunt does not seek or solicit for investment capital or funds of any nature online or via social media sites such as Twitter, Facebook, Instagram or PayPal (or other similar sites), for any of its projects.
If you have any questions regarding the legitimacy or authenticity of any communication, please email your concerns to  fraudalert@huntoil.com.







