Company History 







A Letter From the President

Welcome to the Hunt Oil Company website, where you will find information regarding every aspect of our organization—what we do and where we operate; our mission, core values and leadership; as well as some company events and achievements made public through media releases. You can also read about Hunt's other operations throughout the world and our commitment to both the environment and the communities in which we operate.
Hunt Oil Company is an industry leader in the exploration and production business and other energy-related areas. Over time, we have grown to be one of the largest independent oil and gas companies in the world. Our primary focus is early-stage exploration opportunities, emphasizing idea and prospect generation, establishment of land positions and efficient use of cutting-edge technologies. Our growth vision includes expanding into new geographies as well as exploring and developing newer, unconventional oil and gas projects. We also have deep experience in LNG project development and operations; Hunt is the lead shareholder and operator of the PERU LNG project in Peru and a shareholder in the Yemen LNG project in Yemen.
Hunt Oil Company celebrated its 80th anniversary in 2014. Since 1934, one of our strengths has been to employ extraordinarily talented and motivated people. We strive to provide an exceptional work environment in which our employees' contributions and ideas are both recognized and valued. Our organizational structure is lean and efficient, empowering decision-making throughout all levels of our company. Believing in the power of our people remains a vital element to our company's continued success and longevity.
We encourage you to browse our website, read about our exciting business and learn more about what we do. You'll find that we are in many ways unique, with philosophies that combine old-fashioned principles with modern thinking and technology. It is this varied mix of virtue and ingenuity that will enable us to continue fulfilling our vision to be a growth-oriented industry leader for many years to come.
Sincerely,Steve SuellentropPresidentHunt Oil Company
About Steve Suellentrop









