The Hunt Family of Companies
Hunt Consolidated, Inc. is the flagship entity of the entire Ray L. Hunt family of companies, a privately owned group of entities based in Dallas, Texas. The areas of activity of the different Hunt companies include oil and gas exploration and production, refining, LNG, power, real estate, investments, ranching and infrastructure.
Learn More












Oil & Gas
Hunt has conducted operations worldwide and earned the respect of  the industry as an experienced, capable and cost-effective operator.


more









LNG
Hunt is one of the few independent oil and gas companies with liquefied natural gas projects as a major line of business.


more









Power
Hunt and its affiliates are involved in a variety of innovative activities related to the electric power industry.


more









Real Estate
Hunt has been active in the real estate acquisition, ownership and investment business for more than 30 years.


more









Investments
Hunt has investments in a number of different companies outside of the areas of oil and gas and real estate. The organization operates a family of private equity investment companies.


more









Ranching
Hunt's management company oversees the large-scale land investments of Hunt Consolidated, Inc., Hunt Realty Investments, Inc. and Hunt Oil Company.


more








 
